    "body_html": "<div data-oe-version=\"2.0\">\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"border-style:none;border-left-color:#111827;border-bottom-color:#111827;border-right-color:#111827;border-top-color:#111827;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;caption-side:bottom;border-radius: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: none; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n  <tbody style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#111827;border-bottom-color:#111827;border-right-color:#111827;border-top-color:#111827;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;\">\n    <tr style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#111827;border-bottom-color:#111827;border-right-color:#111827;border-top-color:#111827;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;\">\n      <td align=\"center\" style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#111827;border-bottom-color:#111827;border-right-color:#111827;border-top-color:#111827;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;padding: 20px 0px; background-color: #f2f2f2;\">\n        <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"600\" style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#808080;border-bottom-color:#808080;border-right-color:#808080;border-top-color:#808080;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;caption-side:bottom;border-collapse: collapse; max-width: 600px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6;\">\n          <tbody style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#808080;border-bottom-color:#808080;border-right-color:#808080;border-top-color:#808080;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;\">\n            <tr style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#808080;border-bottom-color:#808080;border-right-color:#808080;border-top-color:#808080;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;\">\n              <td style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#808080;border-bottom-color:#808080;border-right-color:#808080;border-top-color:#808080;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;padding: 20px; background-color: #f2f2f2; color: #101820;\">\n\n                <!-- SAFE VARIABLES (works whether object is hr.applicant, survey.invite, or survey.user_input) -->\n                <t t-set=\"applicant_name\" t-value=\"ctx.get('applicant_name')&#10;                            or (object._fields.get('partner_id') and object.partner_id and object.partner_id.name)&#10;                            or (object._fields.get('partner_name') and object.partner_name)&#10;                            or (object._fields.get('name') and object.name)&#10;                            or 'Applicant'\"/>\n\n                <t t-set=\"job_name\" t-value=\"ctx.get('job_name')&#10;                            or (object._fields.get('job_id') and object.job_id and object.job_id.name)&#10;                            or (object._fields.get('applicant_id') and object.applicant_id and object.applicant_id.job_id and object.applicant_id.job_id.name)&#10;                            or 'Position'\"/>\n\n                <t t-set=\"company_name\" t-value=\"ctx.get('company_name')&#10;                            or (object._fields.get('company_id') and object.company_id and object.company_id.name)&#10;                            or (object._fields.get('job_id') and object.job_id and object.job_id.company_id and object.job_id.company_id.name)&#10;                            or (object._fields.get('applicant_id') and object.applicant_id and object.applicant_id.company_id and object.applicant_id.company_id.name)&#10;                            or 'Our Company'\"/>\n\n                <t t-set=\"survey_link\" t-value=\"ctx.get('technical_test')&#10;                            or ctx.get('survey_link')&#10;                            or ((object._name == 'survey.user_input') and object.get_start_url())&#10;                            or '#'\"/>\n\n                <p style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#101820;border-bottom-color:#101820;border-right-color:#101820;border-top-color:#101820;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;margin:0; padding:0;\">\n                  Dear\n                  <b style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#101820;border-bottom-color:#101820;border-right-color:#101820;border-top-color:#101820;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;font-weight:bolder;\">\n                    <t t-esc=\"applicant_name\"/>\n                  </b>,\n                  <br/><br/>\n                  Thank you for applying for the\n                  <b style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#101820;border-bottom-color:#101820;border-right-color:#101820;border-top-color:#101820;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;font-weight:bolder;\"><t t-esc=\"job_name\"/></b>\n                  position at\n                  <b style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#101820;border-bottom-color:#101820;border-right-color:#101820;border-top-color:#101820;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;font-weight:bolder;\"><t t-esc=\"company_name\"/></b>.\n                  <br/><br/>\n                  We can see that you have already completed assessments for another job position. For this new application, you do not need to retake those.\n                  <br/><br/>\n                  To continue with your application for this role, please complete the assessment specific to this position using the link below.\n                </p>\n\n                <br/>\n\n                <p style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#101820;border-bottom-color:#101820;border-right-color:#101820;border-top-color:#101820;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;margin:0; padding:0;\">\n                  <b style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#101820;border-bottom-color:#101820;border-right-color:#101820;border-top-color:#101820;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;font-weight:bolder;\">What you need to do:</b><br/>\n                  - Please complete the assessment for this position (the estimated time is shown at the start).<br/>\n                  - If you run into any problems, reply to this email and we\u2019ll help.\n                </p>\n\n                <br/>\n\n                <div style=\"padding:16px 8px;\">\n                  <a t-att-href=\"survey_link\" style=\"color: #101820; box-sizing: border-box; border: none; margin: 0px; background-color: #ec008c; text-decoration: none; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold;\">\n                    <span style=\"color:#ffffff; font-weight:700;\">Start Your Assessment</span>\n                  </a>\n                </div>\n\n                <p style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#101820;border-bottom-color:#101820;border-right-color:#101820;border-top-color:#101820;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;margin:0; padding:0;\">\n                  Thank you for your time, and we look forward to reviewing your results.\n                </p>\n\n                <br/>\n\n                <p style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#101820;border-bottom-color:#101820;border-right-color:#101820;border-top-color:#101820;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;margin:0; padding:0;\">\n                  Best regards,<br/>\n                  <b style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#101820;border-bottom-color:#101820;border-right-color:#101820;border-top-color:#101820;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;font-weight:bolder;\">The Recruitment Team</b>\n                </p>\n\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n          </tbody>\n        </table>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n",
    "email_from": "{{ object.company_id.x_studio_short_name }} <{{ object.company_id.alias_domain_id.default_from_email }}>",
